{"id":"fd90ac4758b5478f4213ccb90a128f6fbefc3336e32e9450a49fb8d194649947","item_id":"13d4890951:0","text":"可以通过 RenderMan menu（RenderMan 菜单）下的 Preferences（偏好设置）选项设置多项 RenderMan-specific preferences（RenderMan 专用偏好设置）。"}
{"id":"c7ec711f2017f78d08e98866129fdf470d813d88b968c7ac4c051b26f4b77971","item_id":"13d4890951:1","text":"Live Stats"}
{"id":"5342e09f2729fbc6514528e727aeb9857afb31719d43568e6b18661ace7d1014","item_id":"13d4890951:2","text":"Enable（启用）"}
{"id":"753e604604b912a1775dde3467859fca621c1c466f30121f601147a7c604150a","item_id":"13d4890951:3","text":"启用 Live Stats server（Live Stats 服务器）。"}
{"id":"ea9c4c545092c2c1bc3d3a2623c6a0a42b4696df99cca750659d7f5c72adc559","item_id":"13d4890951:4","text":"Websocket Host（Websocket 主机）"}
{"id":"b4ea1937dec6e9f225b1c283cf5c80e0137d89604dcb784abb2c321d381f22f1","item_id":"13d4890951:5","text":"server（服务器）使用的 host（主机）"}
{"id":"c5e8bf7ae3a67555a451a47bc4a5931ea000c161260b4f1e2fd6711865aa4ac0","item_id":"13d4890951:6","text":"Websocket Port（Websocket 端口）"}
{"id":"eda82c81915a407d3d8d47c98031957b184bd17d3fe8f434621f8bbecf911c15","item_id":"13d4890951:7","text":"server（服务器）使用的 port（端口）"}
{"id":"12fe4737438f3bdbace59e11209e0479d8b7a2fc6022df30d3d54c09988f9667","item_id":"13d4890951:8","text":"Log Level（日志级别）"}
{"id":"d447aa747f2942a4e8f325e2a759b4d701246ef7b722cffcb62ad91f5c5e5fe0","item_id":"13d4890951:9","text":"更改 stats system（统计系统）的 verbosity level（详细程度级别）"}
{"id":"793d90eee5b445e0b7e44294d959956eef966445ca543dc90e7ed822def04daf","item_id":"13d4890951:10","text":"TxManager"}
{"id":"f44944b4e46e51b0fcd24dd34670e5a3f748c352128a4cf2987df1577faa85f3","item_id":"13d4890951:11","text":"Fallback path（回退路径）"}
{"id":"4fa1d0a6647963c45b6b8f39f33a64774509a9fbb4ffd2181f41ca77096578d0","item_id":"13d4890951:12","text":"默认情况下，.tex file（.tex 文件）会写入 source image file（源图像文件）所在的同一目录。如果该目录不可写，texture manager（纹理管理器）会改写入 fallback directory（回退目录）。"}
{"id":"67c8626e86201cd72649761b084e6432997d75f09cc1bf100fa416cb110ad29e","item_id":"13d4890951:13","text":"Tex Extension（Tex 扩展名）"}
{"id":"ead69fdf55d7efd0de2617ead1a611575c1a7b808f5e4d8564ede76304818876","item_id":"13d4890951:14","text":"texture manager（纹理管理器）不会转换带有这些 extensions（扩展名）之一的任何文件，而会按原样使用。各项应以空格分隔"}
{"id":"7a1ec9fe6c3b483f5420a820892c4e29c5e76f6e1bbed4671e07de3371653e98","item_id":"13d4890951:15","text":"Workers（工作进程）"}
{"id":"b42a66106ade14834c1a11ce5e15ec4652462092bf4be36a76675da9a8bf86d1","item_id":"13d4890951:16","text":"并行启动的 txmake processes（txmake 进程）数量。默认值为 2（假设使用典型的 4-core machine，即 4 核机器）。只有在拥有超过 8 个 physical cores（物理核心）时，才应增加该数值。"}
{"id":"c1a9debf3289e60a4542202e5f0ac0f0e28216d22982a60115e5987bdd2c4aa11","item_id":"13d4890951:17","text":"Always Fallback（始终回退）"}
{"id":"cdfd6e3b4b3d54c23c0b6f6a8d430788ae98be59fc4fc67b25246eb9694bac84","item_id":"13d4890951:18","text":"如果此项开启，将只使用 Fallback path（回退路径）选项中指定的目录。"}
{"id":"c62e512e0215ee758318155c48bb73973b53beee680e0f70bdeb1985acad663a","item_id":"13d4890951:19","text":"Keep extension（保留扩展名）"}
{"id":"b3be429db2d3922552355309a8ce123a1deb66c9b6eb375cbbbdbf0fbcfa53fb","item_id":"13d4890951:20","text":"如果开启，则保留 input image（输入图像）的原始 extension（扩展名）"}
{"id":"365075d1bf3ed18878ba0bb50360278b7eaa5973d32ed92fa1544238c09254cb","item_id":"13d4890951:21","text":"Show Advanced（显示高级设置）"}
{"id":"d050ee0a47c2482683529a51ad3f0b128b8c5b4146843af439233f93ea3f273f","item_id":"13d4890951:22","text":"如果开启，则在 Texture Manager panel（Texture Manager 面板）中显示 advanced settings（高级设置）。"}
